u00e9 imersiva e \u00e9 poss\u00edvel desenvolver sistemas de gerenciamento espec\u00edficos e personalizados para os mais variados segmentos, mesmo em \u00e1reas fora do departamento de log\u00edstica.<\/p><p>Os clientes TCIA contam com um parceiro fixo para desenvolver solu\u00e7\u00f5es integradas aos demais sistemas da empresa e totalmente compat\u00edveis com os principais ERPS do mercado.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ac3892e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"ac3892e\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-d715636 ot-flex-column-vertical\" data-id=\"d715636\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-6859202 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"6859202\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-extended\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-29c2c12 ot-flex-column-vertical\" data-id=\"29c2c12\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6545b2 ssub-yes de_scroll_animation_no elementor-widget elementor-widget-iheading\" data-id=\"d6545b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"iheading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ot-heading\">\r\n\t        <span class=\"ot-heading__sub\">MONITORAMENTO INTELIGENTE<\/span>\t        <h2 class=\"ot-heading__title\">Torre de Controle SIAKI<\/h2>\t    <\/div>\r\n\t    \t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2ad16b de_scroll_animation_no elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a2ad16b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Monitoramento Inteligente atrav\u00e9s de sistema de gerenciamento de estoque integrado<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-12580cc de_scroll_animation_no elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"12580cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Muito al\u00e9m da Torre de Controle Log\u00edstico, o SIAKI desenvolvido pela TCIA, \u00e9 um sistema de alta tecnologia para gest\u00e3o de meios e materiais aplicados em cadeias de suprimentos que podem apresentar menor ou maior complexidade de gerenciamento (principalmente no segmento de telecomunica\u00e7\u00f5es). Esta ferramenta se integra facilmente a todos os ERPs dispon\u00edveis no mercado e pode ser totalmente customizada pela equipe TCIA para atender \u00e0s demandas e necessidades de cada neg\u00f3cio.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b5b571 elementor-h